help
.TP
\fB\-r\fR
readonly
.TP
\fB\-t\fR
specify type (VDI, VMDK, VHD, or raw; default: auto)
.TP
\fB\-f\fR
VDimage file
.TP
\fB\-a\fR
allow all users to read disk
.TP
\fB\-w\fR
allow all users to read and write to disk
.TP
\fB\-g\fR
run in foreground
.TP
\fB\-v\fR
verbose
.TP
\fB\-d\fR
debug
.PP
